ji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX9AmLRgh6CWzQqriPxAMnaM9m6m54L2WJBSytWDpzbCB?filename=FWJzphY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWJzphY.png&h=78e32a87&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb7f19eca2734c370c69f72403ed14c40a0b667","tid":2498441,"uid":128102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦&hellip;<br />\n16年前就話蝕俾有車有樓姐<br />\n依家唔知你有無但都唔會衰過16年前掛<br />\n仲煲老藕？16歲就話姐<br />\n條女贏晒永遠拖住個rich既<br />\n你就掛住個已經俾人屌到爛晒年老色衰既發霉肉便器<br />\n真係好肉酸"},{"pid":"b0a1794a1122a0e86a7d74389f52ea7648c56545","tid":2498441,"uid":295630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"聽聽羅生門"},{"pid":"ce99f396b676622cfe75eafbddbba4c17020ba53","tid":2498441,"uid":173817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"做sp正"},{"pid":"7f28e51a8e5656f79e862c6ceca5bb9fdf3870bd","tid":2498441,"uid":156121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"打個飛機冷靜下先啦"},{"pid":"140153136c13eb70ce6c161ca689b17c2f7f19cf","tid":2498441,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:52:16.000Z","msg":"當年佢唔揀你，今日無理由幫佢埋單。"},{"pid":"de4643601ad905faa8b2a4248d5d5ea80edd343f","tid":2498441,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:53:09.000Z","msg":"咪試吓囉 你有冇對象想追 冇咪試吓囉"},{"pid":"dc909274c3724e8056f843c3cbb2127fabb43e71","tid":2498441,"uid":150270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"895a08539166ff3240156ad1d347a0a15f66c0e9","tid":2498441,"uid":184450,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:30:37.000Z","msg":"笑左，垃圾姐係垃圾，16年完全冇進步，個臭西當年前一拖2已經夠差，今時今日人老珠黃，個西比人屌到又黑又反皮，都仲想幫人埋單咁on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過世界總有人中意食n手飯嘅，樓主咁垃圾應該同條女都襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已屌 希望有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講得好 <br />\n樓主我地控制唔到你 不過40歲真係唔好中個頭入去<br />\n唔識下其他？ 三十尾應該都好多人"},{"pid":"de889c6612a6b112d1534e66179c340e15a85ceb","tid":2498441,"uid":260005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"大家到SINGLE冇所謂, 就算當年佢呃過你, 過左16年, 咩到變晒啦.<br />\n你比個機會自己LOR."},{"pid":"1e093bf78d5f0d1f24978d784fb41a4cb699ddd8","tid":2498441,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"問題係邊？ 咁咪試下囉<br />\n買樓咩"},{"pid":"11dc0d93eb710594c58632be5f7ad6f03df93d86","tid":2498441,"uid":242010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"呃得你一次就有第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed300affb197be15bebc1f781b2d1209be93db67","tid":2498441,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c4e76fe4f66b5fa6f2789efab767ded2e7ef6fc","tid":2498441,"uid":298114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"早幾日撞番16年前的女朋友，大家交換左電話，傾左幾日，好似有D仲鍾意佢咁，求屌醒<br />\n<br />\n16年前，出黎做野無耐，去到一間新公司做，同其中一位女同事好傾得埋，一齊放工，食飯咁，之後表白，就係埋一齊了<br />\n<br />\n過左半年左右，我其中一位好熟嘅男同事走黎同我講，見到你女朋友尋晚同另外個男人拖晒手咁去睇戲，當晚收工，我當面問我女朋友，佢呆左一呆，然後承認一直都有男朋友，果個男人年紀大佢一截，但工作好忙，無乜時間陪佢，佢又對我有好感，見我追求佢，佢又同我係埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n果時莫講話Signal，Whatsapp果D，連智能電話都未有，比起宜家，要呃一個人係十分容易，我當時要求佢2揀1，佢喊晒口咁話唔好迫佢，當時我好年青，份糧月月清，根本無錢，而果個男人有車有樓，我根本無得比較，結果我自己退出，然後無耐就遞信辭職了，同佢斷晒聯絡<br />\n<br />\n求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"16 年後... 驅風